{"tid":2208067,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"工會：請假秘撈一向黑箱審批","createTime":"2020-09-18T15:02:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-18T15:02:22.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e13f1cda8e00e6f68ab0b469f278ed26140c7335","tid":2208067,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-18T15:02:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200918/7F7S5ITJJNARPG3OT64ELOBMEY/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200918%2F7F7S5ITJJNARPG3OT64ELOBMEY%2F&d=QA0Qo2zDcB%2FuI%2B3HtJ%2FdCkWuH9aop70KQP2vpO%2BUA2I%3D&h=f2609fa1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200918%2F7F7S5ITJJNARPG3OT64ELOBMEY%2F&h=75b5e91b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200918/7F7S5ITJJNARPG3OT64ELOBMEY/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n工會：請假秘撈一向黑箱審批<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/VzU3MkY0tBqWqJabiI8ff6g6HMQ=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/KGSPPTBV7RFRPC4PFXKXHG4G5U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FVzU3MkY0tBqWqJabiI8ff6g6HMQ%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FKGSPPTBV7RFRPC4PFXKXHG4G5U.jpg&h=78677c3e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】由公務員事務局統籌的全民檢測計劃，由公務員或退休公務員擔任的4,000個檢測中心行政支援人員，被指由三個部門壟斷，遴選準則被質疑模糊不清。公務員工會聯合會總幹事梁籌庭（圖）指出，他雖未有參與今次計劃，但指該類公務員特殊有薪工作由負責統籌計劃的部門全權審批，但審批準則一向欠奉。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：工會：請假秘撈一向黑箱審批<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「我哋無權追問」<br />\n<br />\n梁籌庭昨以不了解全民檢測事件始末為由，不評論事件，但曾擔任選舉工作人員多次的梁，以立法會及區議會選舉為例，指選舉事務處會在政府內部發通函，招募現職公務員擔任選。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n梁續稱，雖然相關負責部門稱以申請者是否有相關工作經驗、居住地點和所揀選的選區是否多人申請，「如果多人申請，佢哋會作出篩選，係抽籤定用乜方法揀選，從來都冇公佈。。。。。。"}]}